@node Main "Whippo - Documentation"

                              'Whippo' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Whippo' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} that is based on the familiar
'sliding-tiles' puzzles. The idea is to move tiles containing
diagonal bars so the number of bars are put in an increasing or
decreasing number from top to bottom. Of course, their colours
must match in each column.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

